{
  "stem": "25348.2",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "But I was cleaning the room of these four Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] And in the evening, when the men came from work, I helped in the kitchen to dish out the, the soups for them and whatever dinner it was.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] From that place, once I looked around and could see what I could steal for my mother, who was starving, I made a few trips to this washer woman.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I forget her name just now.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "It escapes me.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I gave my-- I stole from the Germans for my mother.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "And one day I came, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and this woman was outside.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "When I knocked-- it was a long walk for a little girl to go through a frozen field.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] At home I was scared to go to the toilet at night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] One day, she came out and she said, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] go away, not out of malice, but meaning well.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "My Polish neighbors informed on your mother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "The police took her away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She's not here, and they're waiting for you to denounce you.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] She said that she was brought to the kommandantur, why she-- why, why my mother was in her place.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "My mother, to protect her, must have told her that she had a key and she let herself in.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "So they kept punishing her, why she gave the Jewess the key.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "Anyhow, her son worked for the Germans.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And she was an old lady, so they let her go.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "And she warned me, and I got out.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
